<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Local History</b></p><p>Local History lets you track all changes to files, classes, methods, or any code fragments and roll back to any stable point if necessary. To view local history, from the main menu, select <span class="control">File | Local History | Show History</span>.</p></body></html>